CIC, Blackstone Link to Buy Japan Property Portfolio, FT Reports

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-02-20T21:43:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-20/cic-blackstone-link-to-buy-japan-property-portfolio-ft-reports.html
China Investment Corp. has joined
with  Blackstone Group LP  to buy a Japan property loan portfolio
from  Morgan Stanley  with a face value of $1.1 billion at a
discounted price of 35 cents on the dollar, the Financial Times
reported, citing people familiar with the matter. While the deal
was revealed last year, the fact that CIC was the main party in
the purchase was not disclosed, the FT said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Simpson at 
 jsimpson12@bloomberg.net  